(730, 'HRA 7002 Congratulatory & Condolence', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-S1JjcFRfOVRDeGc', '<p>To express the company&rsquo;s interest in an employee&rsquo;s joy with respect to&nbsp;his / her marriage, birth of child or sorrow in the event of the death of an&nbsp;employee or a member of his / her family and the appropriate sympathy in the event of hospitalization of the employee.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 59, '2016-01-27 09:08:14', '2016-01-27 18:08:14', 'hra-7002-congratulatory-condolence', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(729, 'HRA 7001 Hand Phone', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-SUFtdG5lXzNEN1k', '<p>To prescribe policies and procedures for company hand phone and hand&nbsp;phone claims subsidy.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 59, '2016-01-27 09:07:08', '2016-01-27 18:07:08', 'hra-7001-hand-phone', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(728, 'HRA 6001 Training Policy', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-b080NnpwMlNuM3c', '<p>Professional development and continuous learning are necessary to&nbsp;enhance the capability and quality of the employees by upgrading their&nbsp;competencies. Their continued readiness and ability to contribute effectively to the mission and vision of the company are critical to our Company.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 59, '2016-01-27 09:06:15', '2016-01-27 18:06:15', 'hra-6001-training-policy', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(727, 'HRA 5005 Salary Adjustment', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-N2dMWGZFeTlOXzg', '<p>To establish the criteria for salary adjustment or increment.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 54, '2016-01-27 09:02:42', '2016-01-27 18:02:42', 'hra-5005-salary-adjustment', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(726, 'HRA 5004 Income Tax Clearance', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-Ry1JSmFGWGsxeFE', '<p>The objective of this policy is to ensure that foreign workers clear their&nbsp;Income Tax. Income tax clearance is a process when non-citizen foreign employee pays all taxes when he ceases employment with the Company in Singapore.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 54, '2016-01-27 09:02:03', '2016-01-27 18:02:03', 'hra-5004-income-tax-clearance', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(724, 'HRA 5002 Bonuses ', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-OU12ZDVoNzVmZE0', '<p>To establish the criteria and quantum for the payment of variable bonuses (if any).</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 54, '2016-01-27 09:00:03', '2016-02-16 10:08:34', 'hra-5002-bonuses', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(725, 'HRA 5003 Overtime ', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-VEtKYTBEaHprZXM', '<p>To prescribe policies and procedures for overtime payment.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 54, '2016-01-27 09:01:07', '2016-01-27 18:01:07', 'hra-5003-overtime', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(723, 'HRA 5001 Salary Administration', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-X0R1Ql9vT19LRm8', '<p>To prescribe policies and procedures for salary administration in&nbsp;accordance to Employment Act. Salary refers to the basic monthly wage paid to an employee in conjunction with his / her employment.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 54, '2016-01-27 08:58:34', '2016-01-27 17:58:34', 'hra-5001-salary-administration', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(721, 'HRA 4003 Hospitalisation & Surgical Insurance', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-RC1GZHZqV0xDa0E', '<p>To prescribe policies and procedures for hospitalization and surgical&nbsp;insurance and benefits.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 52, '2016-01-27 08:53:31', '2016-01-27 17:53:31', 'hra-4003-hospitalisation-surgical-insurance', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(722, 'HRA 4004 Accident Death & Dismemberment Insurance', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-NzJmcTZLTmJJXzQ', '<p>To prescribe policies and procedures for accidental death and&nbsp;dismemberment insurance. This coverage is to lessen the financial&nbsp;burden of an employee&rsquo;s dependents in the event of death and or&nbsp;permanent disablement of the employee.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 52, '2016-01-27 08:54:50', '2016-01-27 17:54:50', 'hra-4004-accident-death-dismemberment-insurance', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(720, 'HRA 4002 Work Injury Compensation', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-V2JLUjdrYUg1UFU', '<p>To prescribe policies and procedures for Work Injury Compensation Insurance.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 49, '2016-01-27 08:44:32', '2016-01-27 17:44:32', 'hra-4002-work-injury-compensation', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(719, 'HRA 4001 Outpatient Medical', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-SFlkNkQtcGlKaU0', '<p>To prescribe policies and procedures for outpatient medical benefits.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 49, '2016-01-27 08:43:39', '2016-02-16 10:09:46', 'hra-4001-outpatient-medical-2', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(718, 'HRA 3013 Shared Parental Leave', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-SVc3NXVLQW5DRkE', '<p>This policy sets forth conditions under which an employee is entitled to shared parental leave.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 49, '2016-01-27 08:42:12', '2016-01-27 17:42:12', 'hra-3013-shared-parental-leave', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(717, 'HRA 3012 Infant Care Leave', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-dnJveFlnc0l5Rmc', '<p>This policy sets forth conditions under which an employee is entitled to infant care leave.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 44, '2016-01-27 08:38:54', '2016-01-27 17:38:54', 'hra-3012-infant-care-leave', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(716, 'HRA 3011 Unpaid Leave ', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-QVZWbkJPMGNmYkU', '<p>The objective of this policy is to specify the conditions whereby employees are eligible to apply for No Pay Leave.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 44, '2016-01-27 08:38:15', '2016-02-16 10:09:06', 'hra-3011-unpaid-leave', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(715, 'HRA 3010 Gazetted Public Holiday', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-bndwNFZMQ0VMMWs', '<p>The objective of this policy is to identify the public holidays observed by the company and to describe the eligibility of holiday payments.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 6, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 44, '2016-01-27 08:36:39', '2016-01-27 17:36:39', 'hra-3010-gazetted-public-holiday', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
