(612, 'HRA 6001 Training', 'https://drive.google.com/a/verzdesign.com.sg/file/d/0ByttFUrfYli-b080NnpwMlNuM3c', '<p>Professional development and continuous learning are necessary to&nbsp;enhance the capability and quality of the employees by upgrading their&nbsp;competencies. Their continued readiness and ability to contribute effectively to the mission and vision of the company are critical to our Company.</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 7, 'policy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 59, '2016-01-27 09:06:15', '2016-02-29 09:44:06', 'hra-6001-training', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
