(960, 'Alliance Healthcare Medinet Listing for April 2016', 'New provider listing for Apr''2016 and new online search function on website http://www.alliancehealthcare.com.sg/', '<p>To:&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Client &lt;client@alliancemedinet.com&gt;,<br />\r\nSubject:&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Alliance Healthcare Medinet Prestige Listing for the Month of April 2016</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear All,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To facilitate and enable members to search for clinics nearby, we have built the &ldquo;<b>Search Panel Clinics</b>&rdquo; function on the website: <a href="http://www.alliancehealthcare.com.sg/" onclick="window.open(this.href, '''', ''resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no''); return false;"><b>http://www.alliancehealthcare.com.sg/</b></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simply follow the 3 steps below:<br />\r\n<b>Step 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : Key in NRIC/FIN (eg. S1234567A (No dashes, slashes, spacing or commas between data)<br />\r\nStep 2&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : Select Zone<br />\r\nStep 3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : Click &ldquo;GO&rdquo;</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are also pleased to attach the <b>Provider Listings for the month of Apr 2016</b>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>We strongly urge and would appreciate if company staff can be reminded to always call up respective clinics to confirm that clinic is indeed open and there is a doctor available&nbsp;before making a trip down, to avoid any disappointment.</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><b>MEDINET PRESTIGE PROVIDER LISTING &ndash;APR 2016</b><b>*</b></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For complete listing click here:&nbsp;<a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByttFUrfYli-bGJHMWhzRmRUX1U" onclick="window.open(this.href, '''', ''resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no''); return false;">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByttFUrfYli-bGJHMWhzRmRUX1U</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><i>* Clinic operating hours may change without prior notice.<br />\r\n* Please call clinic before visiting to avoid disappointment as clinics may have unforeseen last-minute changes and/or temporary closure.</i><br />\r\n* <i>Please note that last registration for all clinics is </i><i>30 minutes before closing time, or earlier</i><i> if the number of patients registered exceeds the capacity that the attending doctor and clinic staff can handle without going way beyond standard clinic operating hours.<br />\r\n* Surcharges may be imposed for visits after clinic&#39;s last registration.</i><br />\r\n* <i>Kindly refer to the attached Provider Listing for the addresses and operating hours of the clinics indicated above.</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>1) NEW PANEL CLINICS WITH EFFECT FROM APR 2016</u><br />\r\nGP CLINIC<br />\r\n- MEDILINE WEI MIN CLINIC (BUKIT TIMAH)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>2) CLINICS TERMINATED IN APR 2016</u><br />\r\nGP CLINICS<br />\r\n- MERIDIAN POLYCLINIC &amp; SURGERY<br />\r\n- NUFFIELD MEDICAL SIGLAP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for your kind attention, and have a good day!</p>\r\n', 1, 2, 1, 'announcement', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1460534548_960_alliance_logo.png', 9, '2016-04-13 06:29:36', '2016-04-13 16:02:28', 'alliance-healthcare-medinet-listing-for-april-2016', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
